<p>Currently only covers (shutters in Suplaâ€™s lingo) and switches are supported, but, thanks to comprehensive and universal REST API, itâ€™s pretty easy to add more.</p>
<p>Right now itâ€™s impossible to add single devices â€“ all of them are discovered from Supla Cloudâ€™s servers or yours.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To use Supla devices in your installation, add the following to your <code>configuration.yaml</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">supla:
  servers:
    - server: svr1.supla.org
      access_token: your_really_long_access_token
</code></pre>
